      "line": null,
      "message": "As discussed,\nThe intent of this task (OOM-460)  is to remove the config-init pod configuration and imposing into the container itself, Of-course we need to inject these inputs again as of now, but yes with Standardization HELM task coming our way, we can put all the Openstack Parameters in the common chart as well  and then can impose same wherever used. \n\nSo, It would be taken care with Standardization task once created for Robot.",
